Subject: Re: [eq_wizards] Journal Strongbox Quest (Freeport) *spoiler


what do you get from the quest



At 02:50 PM 7/6/99 -0700, you wrote:

You have to go along the shore to the right of the docks where the boat comes in. There is a lone man fishing there. Swim into the water directly in front of him. There is a lone shark there and the box is underneath it.

Has anybody done the journal strongbox quest in freeport? I keep getting told that the journal strongbox I need to get is in the water by the freeport docks but I cannot find it!
